20static inline isc_result_t
21fromtext_uri(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
22 isc_token_t token;
23
24 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_uri);
25
26 UNUSED(type);
27 UNUSED(rdclass);
28 UNUSED(origin);
29 UNUSED(options);
30 UNUSED(callbacks);
31
32 /*
33 * Priority
34 */
35 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
36 false));
37 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
38 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
39 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
40
41 /*
42 * Weight
43 */
44 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
45 false));
46 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
47 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
48 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
49
50 /*
51 * Target URI
52 */
53 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
54 isc_tokentype_qstring, false));
55 if (token.type != isc_tokentype_qstring)
56 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
57 RETTOK(multitxt_fromtext(&token.value.as_textregion, target));
58 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
59}
60
61static inline isc_result_t
62totext_uri(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
63 isc_region_t region;
64 unsigned short priority, weight;
65 char buf[sizeof("65000 ")];
66
67 UNUSED(tctx);
68
69 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_uri);
70 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
71
72 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
73
74 /*
75 * Priority
76 */
77 priority = uint16_fromregion(&region);
78 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
79 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u ", priority);
80 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
81
82 /*
83 * Weight
84 */
85 weight = uint16_fromregion(&region);
86 isc_region_consume(&region, 2);
87 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u ", weight);
88 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
89
90 /*
91 * Target URI
92 */
93 RETERR(multitxt_totext(&region, target));
94 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
95}

97static inline isc_result_t
98fromwire_uri(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
99 isc_region_t region;
100
101 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_uri);
102
103 UNUSED(type);
104 UNUSED(rdclass);
105 UNUSED(dctx);
106 UNUSED(options);
107
108 /*
109 * Priority, weight
110 */
111 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &region);
112 if (region.length < 4)
113 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
114
115 /*
116 * Priority, weight and target URI
117 */
118 isc_buffer_forward(source, region.length);
119 return (mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
120}

122static inline isc_result_t
123towire_uri(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
124 isc_region_t region;
125
126 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_uri);
127 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
128
129 UNUSED(cctx);
130
131 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
132 return (mem_tobuffer(target, region.base, region.length));
133}

135static inline int
136compare_uri(ARGS_COMPARE) {
137 isc_region_t r1;
138 isc_region_t r2;
139 int order;
140
141 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
142 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
143 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_uri);
144 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
145 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
146
147 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
148 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
149
150 /*
151 * Priority
152 */
153 order = memcmp(r1.base, r2.base, 2);
154 if (order != 0)
155 return (order < 0 ? -1 : 1);
156 isc_region_consume(&r1, 2);
157 isc_region_consume(&r2, 2);
158
159 /*
160 * Weight
161 */
162 order = memcmp(r1.base, r2.base, 2);
163 if (order != 0)
164 return (order < 0 ? -1 : 1);
165 isc_region_consume(&r1, 2);
166 isc_region_consume(&r2, 2);
167
168 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
169}

171static inline isc_result_t
172fromstruct_uri(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
173 dns_rdata_uri_t *uri = source;
174
175 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_uri);
176 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
177 REQUIRE(uri->common.rdtype == type);
178 REQUIRE(uri->common.rdclass == rdclass);
179 REQUIRE(uri->target != NULL && uri->tgt_len != 0);
180
181 UNUSED(type);
182 UNUSED(rdclass);
183
184 /*
185 * Priority
186 */
187 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(uri->priority, target));
188
189 /*
190 * Weight
191 */
192 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(uri->weight, target));
193
194 /*
195 * Target URI
196 */
197 return (mem_tobuffer(target, uri->target, uri->tgt_len));
198}
199
200static inline isc_result_t
201tostruct_uri(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
202 dns_rdata_uri_t *uri = target;
203 isc_region_t sr;
204
205 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_uri);
206 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
207 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
208
209 uri->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
210 uri->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
211 ISC_LINK_INIT(&uri->common, link);
212
213 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
214
215 /*
216 * Priority
217 */
218 if (sr.length < 2)
219 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
220 uri->priority = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
221 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
222
223 /*
224 * Weight
225 */
226 if (sr.length < 2)
227 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
228 uri->weight = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
229 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
230
231 /*
232 * Target URI
233 */
234 uri->tgt_len = sr.length;
235 uri->target = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, sr.length);
236 if (uri->target == NULL)
237 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
238
239 uri->mctx = mctx;
240 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
241}
242
243static inline void
244freestruct_uri(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
245 dns_rdata_uri_t *uri = (dns_rdata_uri_t *) source;
246
247 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
248 REQUIRE(uri->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_uri);
249
250 if (uri->mctx == NULL)
251 return;
252
253 if (uri->target != NULL)
254 isc_mem_free(uri->mctx, uri->target);
255 uri->mctx = NULL;
256}

258static inline isc_result_t
259additionaldata_uri(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
260 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_uri);
261
262 UNUSED(rdata);
263 UNUSED(add);
264 UNUSED(arg);
265
266 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
267}

269static inline isc_result_t
270digest_uri(ARGS_DIGEST) {
271 isc_region_t r;
272
273 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_uri);
274
275 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
276
277 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
278}

306casecompare_uri(ARGS_COMPARE) {
307 return (compare_uri(rdata1, rdata2));
